Body:
If the followers of the Bible would but attain to [true] faith
			and God-consciousness, We should indeed efface their [previous]
			bad deeds, and indeed bring them into gardens of bliss;

And for this their belief <span class='fn'>99</span> God will reward them with
			gardens through which running waters flow, therein to abide: for
			such is the requital of the doers of good;

God has promised unto those who attain to faith and do good works
			[that] theirs shall be forgiveness of sins, and a mighty
			reward;
